msgid "Scenario I: Return to the Gathering"
msgstr "冒险I：重返聚集于此"

msgid "When gathering cards, make the following changes:"
msgstr "在找出卡牌时，进行以下的改变："

msgid "Remove Act 1a- \"Trapped\" from the game and replace it with the new Act 1a- \"Mysterious Gateway.\""
msgstr "从游戏中移除场景1a - ”被困于此”，将其替换为新的场景1a - “神秘通道”。"

msgid "Remove the original Study location from the game and replace it with the new Study <i>Aberrant Gateway</i>."
msgstr "从游戏中移除原版的书房地点，将其替换为新版的书房(异样通道)。"

msgid "Remove the Hallway location from the game."
msgstr "将走廊地点移出游戏。"

msgid "Put Guest Hall, Bedroom, Bathroom and the new Study <i>(Aberrant Gateway)</i> into play. Each investigator begins play in the Study <i>(Aberrant Gateway)</i>."
msgstr "将门厅、卧室、浴室和书房(<i>异样通道</i>)地点放置入场。每位调查员从书房(<i>异样通道</i>)开始游戏。"

msgid "Choose one of the two Attic locations and one of the two Cellar locations at random, and set them aside, out of play. Remove the other versions of Attic and Cellar from the game."
msgstr "随机选择2个阁楼地点之一，2个地窖地点之一。将所选地点放在一边，位于场外。将这些地点的其他所有版本移出游戏。"
